{"tid":1401653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場抗爭要贏,就要識得進化,唔好不停再用一D舊有會輸既戰術","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:17:15.000Z","uid":47905,"like":94,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"637f8ee6117c4515176909a82fe20ddaa30fecc5","tid":1401653,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:00:04.000Z","msg":"我希望前線明白<br />\n<br />\n點解會叫你地散<br />\n因為我地目的係不被捕,不受傷<br />\n你可能會話,我要增加黑警清場難度<br />\n<br />\n咁我同你講,打遊擊,黑警上好裝SET戰術都要幾個鍾<br />\n到佢上晒散就閃,轉場,係第2個場再SET路障,你覺得邊樣難清D?<br />\n玩都玩死佢地啦咁係轉場<br />\n<br />\n你估真係搭車去第2個地區就得?  佢地可能要諗出邊區,係邊度SET防線,點圍<br />\n佢地要傾好撚多野,你地到底明唔明?<br />\n<br />\n不停轉場係先係不受傷不被捕同時又增加黑警清場難度,又無得比佢地打人發洩<br />\n<br />\n再講<br />\n你地唔散,除左比人捉,會少左個手捉,其實支援基金即係又要分擔多一個手足<br />\n每一位手足都唔應該被捕<br />\n<br />\n前線手足依家每次都係同一招,SET路障,死守唔走<br />\n最後速狗過黎打人捉人<br />\n呢個方式每次都輸,每次都有手足比人拉比人打<br />\n都唔轉戰術<br />\n即係你打機卡關,然後會次不斷升級自己既裝備,但你點升都輸,因為依家唔係輸裝備<br />\n係輸戰術呀<br />\n再簡單D講,依家捉緊棋,每次前線都係行個幾步,對家一樣行個幾步<br />\n最後次次比人將軍,結局根本唔會變,明知係死路,你都要繼續行<br />\n轉行其他步好似唔得咁<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏<br />\n就要識得進化,唔好不停再用一D舊有會輸既戰術"},{"pid":"de1463ca1f865b33ceca2cda5aff336bc1a8e225","tid":1401653,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:02:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db3872e7b52a0dbdd0e11c1b5581d16db4f1bdd","tid":1401653,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ae0356c2db4342e52307893a97fb9b738b951b","tid":1401653,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab352e010ec7ad090e69122955bc7f61a1888985","tid":1401653,"uid":132625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"講得好<br />\n革命要有兵法<br />\n唔係口講有腦 行動冇腦<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東教落：「打得贏就打，打不贏就跑，跑不贏就鑽，鑽不贏就化。」<br />\n<br />\n唔想一齊爬山的嘅兄弟要坐十碌啊<br />\n唔想兄弟少吓一個 少吓又一個啊<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"53bb5ec167a2bbe5bf262f252d4894016619b2e1","tid":1401653,"uid":239994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"醒目、醒水"},{"pid":"a53d72b934a94da5241a54dda2df3d5c5323b1b5","tid":1401653,"uid":12426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">明顯有狗扮示威者<br />\n引你地留低</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b2ef14937cdb262c43b7c75a6f290ed83041914","tid":1401653,"uid":275588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db793f9335899beb840269cc08c2204a1afc2e5a","tid":1401653,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"05d673698fb11d32c53b41ba8ee3aadc9e2310df","tid":1401653,"uid":106252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9caf4a230848cdc6bce5e6e71f9f49edfd9e7f66","tid":1401653,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:15:52.000Z","msg":"不被捕 不受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f4aea950d9e4052f15f5e714a2348a0579f964","tid":1401653,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"[建議]關於罷買！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1401281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1401281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fbd0ae7f8a5416cb7b4aeb3f8b5eb6c3c717145e","tid":1401653,"uid":186283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:10.000Z","msg":"Winter on fire. <br />\nNo pain No gain."},{"p