\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒就推埋其他文宣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線要打仗 網絡文宣都要打仗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[文宣] 點解要罷工 瘋傳比d唔知罷黎做咩既人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1397455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1397455</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XcoQUfO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcoQUfO.png&h=ec474b03&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kB299O8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkB299O8.png&h=5ec7dc0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/apgbDHt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FapgbDHt.png&h=0d769dcc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv7Wt9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv7Wt9.png&h=83af85ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmXBPO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmXBPO9.png&h=317787c2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}